title: List of U.S. Highways in Florida
text: The U.S. Highways in Florida are the segments of the <a href="United%20States%20Numbered%20Highway%20System">United States Numbered Highway System</a> maintained by the <a href="Florida%20Department%20of%20Transportation">Florida Department of Transportation</a> (FDOT). Prior to 1993, Florida used colored shields for its U.S. Highways.
